               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Zarʾa Buruk “Miracles of Zarʾa Buruk”: 23 miracles (fols.
                     5ra-68vb) 
 II) Malkǝʾa Zarʾa Buruk “Image of Zarʾa Buruk” (fols.
                     69ra-75rb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
